    "body": "i am trying to create a multi-line textbox to input the numbers of contacts instead of using the the add-on input in the whatsapp.php web client , the problem is that i have tested adding the text box and i chose a number from the add-on and entered another number in the text box it sent the message for both numbers, the question is when i try to add 2 or three numbers in the text box beneath each other it doesnt send to any number of entered, so how can i get it to read the numbers in the textbox in each line.\r\n\r\nand how can i add the option of creating groups directly into the whatsapp.php file\r\nhelp is kindly appreciated",
